entry.title: For Palestinians Trapped in Gaza, There Is No Way Out
entry.content: Palestinians and foreign nationals in the Gaza Strip are trying to flee to safety ahead of an anticipated Israeli ground invasion but are finding there is nowhere to run.

entry.title: Israel Aims to Dismantle Hamas as Blinken Tries to Prevent Wider War
entry.content: Secretary of State Antony Blinken urged Israel to avoid civilian casualties amid growing fears of a wider regional conflict as Israel pounded Gaza with airstrikes.
